<br />
WoW basically has very little end-game and their servers are unstable/overloaded to the point of unplayability during peak hours. I'm sure those two things are contributing to a fair number of people leaving...</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"></td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
